import React from 'react';
import { Form, Card, Col, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

class Student extends React.Component {

    constructor (props) {
        super (props);
        this.state = {lastName:'', firstName:'', IdCard:'', phoneNr:'', paymentStatus:'', lessonHrs:'', unpaidLessons:'', moneyOwing:'', paymentInAdvance:''}
    }

    render() {
        return (
            <Card className={"border border-dark bg-dark text-white"}>
                <Form >
                    <Form.Row>
                        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridLastName">
                            <Form.Label>Last Name</Form.Label>
                            <Form.Control type="lastName" placeholder="Enter Last Name"
                                className={"bg-dark text-white"} />
                        </Form.Group>

                        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridFirstName">
                            <Form.Label>First Name</Form.Label>
                            <Form.Control type="firstName" placeholder=" Enter First Name"
                                className={"bg-dark text-white"} />
                        </Form.Group>
                    </Form.Row>

                    <Form.Row>

                        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridIdCard">
                            <Form.Label>IdCard</Form.Label>
                            <Form.Control type="IdCard" placeholder="Enter Id Card"
                                className={"bg-dark text-white"} />
                        </Form.Group>

                        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridPhoneNr">
                            <Form.Label>Phone Nr</Form.Label>
                            <Form.Control type="phoneNr" placeholder="Enter Phone Nr"
                                className={"bg-dark text-white"} />
                        </Form.Group>
                    </Form.Row >


                    <Form.Row>

                        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridPaymentInAdvance">
                            <Form.Label>Payment In Advance [zl]</Form.Label>
                            <Form.Control type="Payment In Advance" placeholder="$"
                                className={"bg-dark text-white"} />
                        </Form.Group>

                    </Form.Row >



                    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                        Submit
                    </Button>
                </Form >

            </Card>
        );
    }

}
export default Student;
